@startuml
skinparam actorStyle awesome
actor "Handler of Start" as Start <<Strategic>>
actor "Handler of Conflicts" as Conflicts <<Governance>>
actor "Handler of Exceptions" as Exceptions <<Tactical>>
participant "AI Orchestrator" as AI <<Operational>>
actor "Delivery Specialist" as Delivery <<Technical>>

== Starting Decision ==
Start -> AI: Authorization to Invest
note right: Outputs: Project Vision,\nBusiness Case

== Alignment Decision ==
AI -> Conflicts: Request Alignment
Conflicts -> AI: Commitment to Scope & Priorities
note right: Outputs: Strategic Backlog,\nGovernance Guardrails

== Execution Loop ==
loop continuous delivery
    AI -> Delivery: Orchestrate Tasks
    Delivery -> AI: Deliver Increment
    note right: Outputs: Increment,\nOperational Plan
    AI -> AI: Check Tolerances & Observability

    alt Out of Tolerance (Exception)
        AI -> Exceptions: Alert / Flag Exception
        Exceptions -> AI: Course Correction / Pivot
        note right: Outputs: Risk Register,\nTolerance Baseline
    end
end

== Realization Decision ==
AI -> Start: Realization Evidence
Start -> AI: Authorization of Closure
note right: Outputs: Quality & Compliance\nEvidence
@enduml
